      <title>eBay 将裁员 1,000 人，减少承包商以集中精力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/ebay-to-cut-1-000-jobs-reduce-contractors-to-sharpen-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[eBay Inc. 将裁员约 1,000 人，即全职员工的 9%，并减少外部承包商的工作量，称人员配置和费用增长速度超过了增长速度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/ebay-to-cut-1-000-jobs-reduce-contractors-to-sharpen-focus</guid>
